text: Aur mote bhai, apan to 6 saal se sath the yrr. apni memory bhi kaafi hai bas itna hi kehna chahunga ki treat pizza bas ki nhi hoti hai kabhi kabhi roll me bhi kaam chalana hota hai. MIlte hai teri shaadi mein.
author: Ramsharan  Ahirwar

text: Hello dost, Crypto me A lagwaya bhai tumne. Aur to koi memory nhi hai.
author: Ramsharan  Ahirwar

text: hey yashika, waise apni jyada memory to nhi hai. Fir bhi jitna janta hu us hisaab se tum talented to ho hi aur dance bahut achha kar leti ho, aur always ready for help. Milte hai kabhi dakshana reunion me ya fir jab kismat milaye.
author: Ramsharan  Ahirwar
